Historic Districts in the City of St. Louis

A simple features data set containing polygons for the major bodies of water in the city.

data(stl_sf_historic)

Format

A simple feature with 102 rows and 6 variables:

NUMBER

District number

NAME

District name

LAYER

District type

COUNT

count

DATE

District creation date

geometry

simple features geometry
